{"tid":1242463,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"其隱藏回覆係玩鳩緊連登自己","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T17:51:16.000Z","uid":15644,"like":17,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fe94d86a906328411dbd090c1545649311cc3b7a","tid":1242463,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"我好記得上高登既時間大約2002年既時候<br />\n果時一開始我都acc <br />\n做左幾年cd rom<br />\n但係果陣高登真係開左我呢個死o靚仔眼界<br />\n<br />\n敢問連登而家玩隱藏回覆係所謂何事?<br />\n杜絕cd-rom? 有必要嗎?<br />\n長遠只會影響發展<br />\n好多人想睇 想了解<br />\n但係伸請唔到 唔識伸請<br />\n但特別係出左黎社會做野 又無isp email<br />\n而家連比佢地睇內容既機會都剝削<br />\n好多po 佢地都睇到R 唒頭唔知講緊乜<br />\n最後佢地為有離開<br />\n咁 又有意思咩?"},{"pid":"a8187e19be362bec39a7a32d036f65f3547e673d","tid":1242463,"uid":156130,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:21:03.000Z","msg":"慢慢伸，唔阻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c8cc04494f6b5ab9f85e47c2e5178f6e34d0fc","tid":1242463,"uid":29080,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aeffc474cc02ff82387b13c2d97e16402117f50","tid":1242463,"uid":142878,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"好多錯字"},{"pid":"5e0fff6c4845f0cc97aece430800b358e01b6904","tid":1242463,"uid":36489,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:33:28.000Z","msg":"我認同呀，身邊好多前線義士都係 cd rom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bfd7262f7e48a72a4fddc9536b6cf8ba302f81","tid":1242463,"uid":15644,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5e0fff6c4845f0cc97aece430800b358e01b6904","tid":1242463,"u